    <div class="w-full relative py-8 px-4 flex flex-col gap-8 justify-between md:grid md:grid-cols-12">
        <h1
            class="text-white italic text-base underline underline-offset-8 tracking-widest text-xl left-4 z-10 md:col-start-3 md:col-span-8 lg:col-start-3 lg:col-span-8">
            "Background"
        </h1>

        <p
            class="text-sm font-semibold italic leading-7 tracking-wider text-white z-10 text-justify md:col-start-3 md:col-span-8 lg:col-start-3 lg:col-span-8 text-justify">
            Since the
            military
            seized
            sovereignty in
            Myanmar on February 1, 2021, Myanmar has committed violent
            repression, unlawful killings, and violations of basic human rights and labor rights against the entire
            indigenous population. They have been victims of violence and rights violations, such as torture, coercion,
            unwarranted arrest of employers, dissolution of company operations and confiscation of property, and
            unlawful collection and embezzlement of military council employees.

            Businessmen who do not want the military dictatorship have joined hands with the people in Myanmar's
            democracy movements, and have been forced to flee to various peaceful liberations due to violent arrests by
            the military group.The Federation of Myanmar Businessmen's Union was formed on October 14, 2024.</p>
